---
title: Mediterranean Beef & Cheese Meatballs with Herbed Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt Dressing
description: Get a load of this meal that's brimming with colour and flavour. With a herb-packed couscous, mildly spiced beef
meatballs and a creamy lemon yoghurt dressing, all the elements come together for a delightful explosion of taste!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-feta-meatballs-tabbouleh-31646121.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/beef-feta-meatballs-tabbouleh-603345bf8e97ec5a00385936-afcb8938.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
